        <title type="html"><![CDATA[Codeforces 29 A 题解]]></title>
        <id>https://david9006.github.io/post/codeforces-29-a-ti-jie/</id>
        <link href="https://david9006.github.io/post/codeforces-29-a-ti-jie/">
        </link>
        <updated>2022-05-05T13:09:16.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>（题目链接：https://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/29/A）<br>
（我的提交：https://codeforces.com/contest/29/submission/155919409）</p>
<h2 id="1-题意">1. 题意</h2>
<p>在一个动物园里，有很多骆驼。众所周知，骆驼喜欢吐口水。Bob花了一整天看他们吐口水，并且在他的笔记本上记下了每只骆驼在吐口水时所在的位置。现在，他想知道有没有一对骆驼互相向对方吐口水。</p>
<p>如果一只骆驼在 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>(</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mn>0</mn><mn>4</mn></msup><mo>≤</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>≤</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mn>0</mn><mn>4</mn></msup><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x (-10^4 \le x \le 10^4)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.064108em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">x</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">0</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8141079999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">4</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≤</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7719400000000001em;vertical-align:-0.13597em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">x</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≤</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.064108em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">0</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8141079999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">4</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span> 位置吐出了 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>d</mi><mo>(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>≤</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mo>≤</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mn>0</mn><mn>4</mn></msup><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">d (1 \le |d| \le 2 \times 10^4)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≤</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≤</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.72777em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">×</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.064108em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">0</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8141079999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">4</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span> 长度的口水，则吐出的口水只会打到 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>d</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(x + d)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">x</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span> 位置的骆驼。</p>
<h2 id="2-思路">2. 思路</h2>
<ul>
<li>首先，我们用一个结构体或一个<code>std::pair</code>把所有骆驼存下来；</li>
<li>用一个双重循环遍历所有骆驼，把正在遍历的两个骆驼进行判断：它们两个是否在互吐口水；</li>
<li>按照第二步的判断结果来相应输出<code>YES</code>或<code>NO</code>。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="3-代码">3. 代码</h2>
<pre><code class="language-cpp">// Codeforces Beta Round #29 (Div. 2, Codeforces format) - A. Spit Problem
#include &lt;iostream&gt;
#include &lt;vector&gt;

#define OPTIMIZE() do {             \
    ios::sync_with_stdio(false);    \
    cin.tie(nullptr);               \
    cout.tie(nullptr);              \
} while (0);

using namespace std;

struct Camel {
    int pos, spit_len;
};

int main() {
    OPTIMIZE();

    int n;
    vector&lt;Camel&gt; camels;

    cin &gt;&gt; n;
    camels.resize(n);

    for (auto&amp; camel : camels) {
        cin &gt;&gt; camel.pos &gt;&gt; camel.spit_len;
    }

    // 用双重循环挨个遍历所有骆驼
    for (int i = 0; i &lt; n; ++i) {
        for (int j = i + 1; j &lt; n; ++j) {
            if (camels[i].pos + camels[i].spit_len == camels[j].pos &amp;&amp; camels[j].pos + camels[j].spit_len == camels[i].pos) {
                cout &lt;&lt; &quot;YES&quot; &lt;&lt; endl;
                return 0;    // 只要找到答案，就立刻退出程序，不然还会输出一遍&quot;NO&quot;
            }
        }
    }
    
    cout &lt;&lt; &quot;NO&quot; &lt;&lt; endl;
    return 0;
}
</code></pre>
]]></content>
